                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-lg-3">
                        <div class="panel-Faq">
                            <div class="panel-Faq-Header">How does MCA<sup>®</sup> provide creative quality and impact to business?</div>
                            <div class="panel-Faq-Body">Agencies typically struggle to find ways to show the true value of their creative output, i.e. what is it delivering to the business, is it better than previous work, is it winning versus competitors, is it building better consumer journeys? MCA<sup>®</sup> metrics provide transparency of what's working and what's not providing line-of-sight from marcoms to business performance. Touchpoint performance versus competitors provide insights into what individual creative is working well versus less well, prompting follow-up into consumer response to creative strategy and execution.</div>
